title: Ep. - 183 - WELLS ADAMS FROM BACHELOR IN PARADISE
description:
Wells Adams is the bartender and resident therapist this season on ABC’s Bachelor in Paradise, which is a show about rejects from The Bachelor and The Bachelorette and their pursuit for true love.


Rabbi Corie Yutkin reviews the documentary One Of Us, a a 2017 documentary feature film that chronicles the lives of three ex-Hasidic Jews from Brooklyn.


Kardashian superman Colt Paulsen reviews the season premiere of Keeping Up With the Kardashians.
